name: The Seattle - Wallet
description:
100% Made with my own two hands in the USA. 
The Seattle, features a rich coffee brown stain and plaid interior lining. Made from heavy weight cow hide and stitched with rugged gold thread (like your favorite combat boots). This wallet features the Engraved Rock and Ride design etched deep into the cover, while the interior will hold all your important paper, cards, and ID. No worries on losing control over your goods with the snap closure. 
Available with or with out a 20" Ball Chain
Being a hand made product each wallet comes has its own unique variations giving it extra personality.

name: Rock and Ride - Pin-up Helmet - Custom Hand Painted
description:
Custom hand Pained Helmet, and distressed look. A Rock and Ride exclusive design. Does it look familiar? So here is the story, Josh made me a helmet with a pin-up on one side and 11 on the other with some racing strips down the center. Everyone that saw it wanted it... So Abby suggested we design a shirt similar to it. As soon as we released the Pin-Up / Helmet t-shirt someone bought the original helmet, so Josh was kind enough to make us another but this time it was made to look more like the shirt. I love it, its brand new, never worn, and can be yours today.

This is painted on a Flat Black Biltwell NON-DOT 3/4 helmet.

Painting done but one of the top custom painters and good friend, Josh School at Old School Helmets.
http://www.digthelid.com

description:
Our hearts race with a passion for motorcycles, and with every turn of the wrench it is our soul that becomes customized. We took the traditional Sacred Heart and mashed it up with some mechanical steam punk style to symbolize this truth.

This design is hand screen printed in Pittsburgh, PA on Black Hanes Beefy T-shirts that are 100% ring spun cotton (super soft).

Orders generally ship the following business day via USPS. 
Let us know if you don’t see your size available.

description:

name: Willow -  Full Zip Hoodie
description:
Limited Edition, Hand Crafted, High-End Full Zip Hoodie. If your not familiar with the name sake, hand build Custom Motorcycle "Willow", Look (google / youtube) it up its one amazing machine. I spend a lot of time hand crafting this piece to make sure the quality and attention to detail did justice to the bike it featured, plus the lady is a nice bonus. With a custom cut red twill "Rock and Ride" script across the full zip chest that featured the speedometer from Willow screen printed in the background.

Above is an interview with my buddy Troy who built Willow by hand. Hover over video to access the full screen mode. Video made possible my MotoPickers.com, the interviewd Troy in the Rock and Ride booth at Timionium.

name: Brittown - DVD
description:
This is a great flick, if you are into British bikes you will definitely enjoy! From One World Studios:


The new film from the directors of the award-winning custom motorcycle documentary Choppertown... Brittown features Meatball from the Hell On Wheels bike shop in Anaheim, CA.

As a master mechanic, vintage Britbike connoisseur and motorcycle racer, Meatball splits his time between family, his shop and his rock band Smiling Face Down.

Join Meatball for several months as he runs his old BSA in vintage motocross races, hits the desert with the No Gooders bike club, flies down the Willow Springs straightaways on his Norstar, and uses all his skill to rebuild an old 650 Triumph Bonneville motor into a blazing road-ready screamer.

Featuring an insider's view of the SoCal Britbike culture including vintage motocross, dirt track, road racing, custom street bikes, and even a wild vintage lingerie beauty contest! Brittown is a ride you won't soon forget.

All region DVD with bonus clips and 12 page full-color booklet.

This film is not rated. Adult themes, strong language, scantily-clad girls.

name: Biltwell "Novelty" Helmets Mega Flake (All 11 Colors)
description:
Biltwell Mega Flake lids have biggest, brightest metal flake paint available. These things pop like crazy and are as comfortable as they are good looking. The liner is completely removable and washable.

A word about sizing. Miraculously, the Biltwell helmet is one size fits most. Medium helmet-wearers and their size 8+ pals can squeeze their melons into our helmet without discomfort. That’s because the foam padding inside our helmets is really soft and compliant, and because the outer shell is so flexible. Of course, this is the reason why the this Biltwell helmet is designed for novelty purposes only, and should never be worn to operate an actual motorcycle. Simply put, this helmet do not meet any DOT or other safety standards.

name: Biltwell "Novelty" Helmets Flat & Gloss (All 12 Colors)
description:
The same helmet shell, liner and chrome trim as the Mega Flakes, but with a more low-key vibe. These things are as comfortable as they are good looking. The liner is completely removable and washable.

A word about sizing. Miraculously, the Biltwell helmet is one size fits most. Medium helmet-wearers and their size 8+ pals can squeeze their melons into our helmet without discomfort. That’s because the foam padding inside our helmets is really soft and compliant, and because the outer shell is so flexible. Of course, this is the reason why the this Biltwell helmet is designed for novelty purposes only, and should never be worn to operate an actual motorcycle. Simply put, this helmet do not meet any DOT or other safety standards.

name: Biltwell "DOT" Bonanza Helmets (All 8 Colors)
description:
PRE-ORDER NOW!

we’re changing the game again with our brand-new Bonanza helmet. This leaner, lighter and even more comfortable DOT-approved 3/4 lid boasts the same hand-painted finishes as our other lids on an even lower-profile molded ABS shell. The Bonanza's interior boasts a custom-shaped EPS safety shell and a hand-stitched liner with moisture wicking brushed Lycra panels and open-cell foam padding for breathability and comfort. The rugged nylon neck strap features plated steel D-rings and a snap strap end retainer with Biltwell anvil branding.

Available in six sizes, XS-XXL, there's a Biltwell Bonanza helmet to fit everyone's individual head and style.

X Small - 20 1/4" - 20 3/4" Small - 20 7/8" - 21 3/8" Medium - 21 1/2" - 22" Large - 22 1/8" - 22 5/8" X Large - 22 3/4" - 23 1/4" XX Large - 23 3/8" - 23 7/8"

description: With the adjustable, sliding snaps, these bubble shields by Biltwell, Inc. will fit most brands of open face 3/4 helmets, including Biltwell novelty and Bonanza DOT helmets, Bell and Fulmer.

name: Bubble Shield - Gradient & Mirror (Mirror / Smoke / Red / Blue / Green)
description: With the adjustable, sliding snaps, these bubble shields by Biltwell, Inc. will fit most brands of open face 3/4 helmets, including Biltwell novelty and Bonanza DOT helmets, Bell and Fulmer.

name: Moto Riding Goggles - (Black / White / Grey)
description: The guys at Biltwell dug deep into their old motocross roots to reissue this classic piece of performance eyewear. Biltwell Moto Goggles boast state-of-the-art construction and technology, but feature toned-down styling and colors for modern bikeriders. The molded frame features a large eye port for excellent peripheral visibility. Two-stage foam with fleece outer layer provides venting and comfort, and the clear anti-fog lens is removable for cleaning and replacement. The heavy-duty strap on Moto Goggles is woven for superior stretch and durability, and features double D-rings for precise adjustment.
